      "rationale": "All three FEA solvers (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under formal software quality assurance plans. Ansys holds ISO 9001 certification and provides a product validation report. FDA solver is governed by CDRH OSEL SQA procedures with version-controlled regression tests. Achieved Gradation 2 satisfies required level for Model Risk 3, Medium influence COU."
