      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions and material properties demonstrably equivalent to experimental setup; torque application and fixation conditions matched.",
      "rationale": "Experimental fixation torque (4 Nm per screw) was replicated in FEA via pretension bolt elements. Loading fixture geometry was reproduced from engineering drawings. CMM-verified screw geometry was used for both test and simulation. Equivalency table mapping each experimental parameter to its FEA counterpart was reviewed and approved."
    },
